com.interpss.core.aclf.adpter

Interface AclfXformer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AclfBranchAdapter, BranchRef<AclfBranch>, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AclfPSXformer, AcscPSXformer, AcscXformer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfPSXformerImpl, AclfXformerImpl, AcscPSXformerImpl, AcscXformerImpl

    public interface AclfXformer
extends AclfBranchAdapter
    A representation of the model object 'Xfr Adapter'. An adapter to convert an AclfBranch object to an Aclf Xfr branch.
    See Also:
    AclfObjAdapterPackage.getAclfXformer()
